<section sectnbr = "8B">
<servcat sctnbr = "08" scnbr = "02">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "4">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70A8204044" svcinfotypenbr = "06" svcinfoqualnbr = "02" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
DTC B1302
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A8204044001">
<title>
DTC Detecting Condition and Trouble Area
</title>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "4.665in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.512in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
DTC detecting condition
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Trouble area
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
B1302: Passenger Cut Off SW Detected
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Wrong SDM (without passenger air bag deactivation switch) is installed on vehicle (with passenger air bag deactivation switch).
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
SDM
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
When SDM without passenger air bag deactivation switch is installed in the vehicle with passenger air bag deactivation switch, this DTC is set. Replace with the correct SDM.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
